archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: Security Architecture Review (SAR) Service Realization
archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation:
The Security Architecture Review Service provides a way for us to assess quality and work happening within Tietoevry Tech Services.
Essentially the service is comprised of two levels of architecture review (Known as SAR1 and SAR2). Both reviews have automation sat behind them and begin with architects beginning a self-assessment.
To aid in the completion of the forms a Security Architecture Review Guide is published with a lot of detail on every question, including what the questions are, why we ask them, and how we assess them.
